          "id": "40faad9c9d812e853eef82066f2ac87514c09840",
          "message": "Imports subtrees (#158)\n\nAdds a new macro `\\agda-imports` for a folded-by-default subtree with the imports of each module.\nThe agda imports block should not contain imports that rename entries, `Axiom` imports, or definitions.\n\nThe only agda files that do not have an agda imports block now are:\n\n```text\nsrc/Axioms/UF.lagda.tree\nsrc/Foundations/Universes.lagda.tree\nsrc/Foundations/Prelude.lagda.tree\nsrc/Foundations/Reasoning.lagda.tree\n```\n\nAdditionally,\n- Minimizes the foundations imports that happen before the main module declaration, to make it easier to see what's needed for the module declaration itself.\n- Removes the distributivity assumption on lattices where not needed, which is everywhere.\n- Assumes a cohesive interval also in `Synthetic.Categories.UniversalElements`, like everywhere else.\n- Removes some redundant imports and sorts the `Foundations.Prelude` file.\n\nBuilds on #156. Resolves #64. \n\n------\n\n* add pre-commit\n\n* bump `actions/cache` version to 5\n\n* run pre-commit\n\n* ignore `theme` for codespell\n\n* more hooks!\n\n* run pre-commit again\n\n* fix shell lint\n\n* empty commit\n\n* capitalization\n\n* add `\\imports` macro\n\n* use `\\imports` macro\n\n* fixes to many module shenanigans\n\n* fix merge\n\n* move renaming and private declarations out of `\\imports`\n\n* remove unused `private` declarations\n\n* pre-commit\n\n* simplify some equalities\n\n* have imports in ToC\n\n* add imports block to new modules\n\n* rename `\\imports` to `\\agda-imports` to disambiguate from `\\import`\n\n* remove `open is-distributive` in `Synthetic.Categories`\n\n* only import necessary foundations before module declaration\n\n* assume cohesive interval in `Synthetic.Categories.UniversalElements`\n\n* `let open` -> `open`\n\n* remove distributivity assumption in `Synthetic.Categories`\n\n* add `TotalEquiv` to prelude\n\n* move `Axioms.UF` out of `agda-imports` block\n\n* remove some redundant imports\n\n* fix `Prelude` import `Synthetic.Hom`\n\n* remove duplicate imports\n\n* sort prelude\n\n* restore autogenerated nix files\n\n* review",
          "timestamp": "2026-06-03T14:21:06+02:00",
          "tree_id": "4d726f23d2830710440f27516d865db858039983",
          "url": "https://github.com/samtoth/agda-synthetic-categories/commit/40faad9c9d812e853eef82066f2ac87514c09840"
